# Skills language

- All **Cursor Agent Skills** under any `.cursor/skills/**/SKILL.md` in this workspace must be written in **English** (titles, body, examples, checklists).
- When editing or creating skills, translate non-English content to English; keep code paths, package names, and imports unchanged.
